renegotiate our contract,
don't you?

01:27:58.399 --> 01:28:02.362
Yes, I do.
I agree with you completely.

01:28:02.987 --> 01:28:05.949
What would you say to

01:28:06.157 --> 01:28:10.119
one third of %8 million?

01:28:10.328 --> 01:28:12.038
Would you say that's fair?

01:28:12.246 --> 01:28:14.123
I'd say that that's extremely--

01:28:25.551 --> 01:28:26.636
What just happened?

01:28:27.929 --> 01:28:31.349
I turned out the lights,
just for a moment.

01:28:31.557 --> 01:28:34.018
