to gain the advantage.

01:28:36.062 --> 01:28:40.066
I get the feeling I'm not the only
blind person in this room.

01:28:40.483 --> 01:28:43.194
You have great intuition,
Mr. Kerew.

01:28:43.903 --> 01:28:47.490
