to lock in on poor Mr. Kirgo.

01:28:52.704 --> 01:28:53.913
It's too bad.

01:28:54.122 --> 01:28:57.583
I liked him. He was a gentleman.

01:28:57.750 --> 01:29:00.336
I can't see,
but I bet you're not crying.

01:29:00.503 --> 01:29:03.631
Nor can I see your face,
Mr. Kerew,

01:29:04.298 --> 01:29:07.760
yet I can hear you stoop down
to find Kirgo's pistol.

01:29:08.928 --> 01:29:10.596
Am I right, sir?

01:29:11.014 --> 01:29:13.933
Must I put a bullet
through you to prove it?

01:29:14.100 --> 01:29:16.436
Oh, no. You're a gentleman.
Get him.

01:29:16.602 --> 01:29:19.605
One murder a day is enough for you.
Get him.

01:30:07.320 --> 01:30:10.948
Did I hear something drop,
Mr. Kerew?

01:30:20.083 --> 01:30:24.170
Mr. Sutherland?
Perfect timing. Come in, my dear.

01:30:24.378 --> 01:30:26.172
