01:30:26.380 --> 01:30:27.507
Wally.

01:30:28.257 --> 01:30:29.967
Are you all right?

01:30:31.302 --> 01:30:33.304
You're very quiet, Mr. Kerew.

01:30:33.471 --> 01:30:36.641
