to renegotiate his contract

01:30:53.991 --> 01:30:56.536
and he put a pistol to my head.

01:30:56.702 --> 01:30:59.247
Eve, we've been associated
for five years.

01:30:59.413 --> 01:31:02.208
I want you to know
I have no intention
of killing you.

01:31:03.626 --> 01:31:05.128
So don't be frightened, dear.

01:31:05.294 --> 01:31:08.381
And, please,
don't do anything rash.

01:31:08.631 --> 01:31:13.719
Oh. No, I wouldn't do that.
You know I trust you,
Mr. Sutherland.

01:31:14.303 --> 01:31:16.347
But what are your intentions?

01:31:16.722 --> 01:31:20.560
To leave the country as soon
as Raoul sets my helicopter down.

01:31:20.726 --> 01:31:22.895
I invite you to come along.

01:31:23.062 --> 01:31:26.023
Rio can be captivating
this time of year.

01:31:26.899 --> 01:31:29.193
Just pick up the gold coin

01:31:29.402 --> 01:31:33.072
I believe is on the floor
in front of you.

01:31:37.410 --> 01:31:38.411
