01:31:55.761 --> 01:31:57.263
Yes, I found it.

01:31:58.055 --> 01:32:01.517
Would you hand it to me, please?

01:32:03.603 --> 01:32:05.897
May I ask what my share might be?

01:32:07.648 --> 01:32:08.858
One...

01:32:09.901 --> 01:32:13.529
